videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson gets the rebound and goes the length of the court for the layup.
videos.headline: UConn's Samuelson goes coast to coast for the layup

videos.description: Saniya Chong gets the steal and Naphessa Collier scores on the fast break.
videos.headline: UConn gets the steal and scores the layup on the break

videos.description: Naphessa Collier blocks the shot and Crystal Dangerfield takes it all the way for the layup.
videos.headline: UConn turning defense into offense with the Dangerfield layup

videos.description: Saniya Chong gets the steal and the Huskies uses some good ball movement for the Katie Lou Samuelson  3-pointer.
videos.headline: UConn gets the steal and uses some good passing for the 3 pointer

videos.description: Kia Nurse gets the rebound and throws a pass to Katie Lou Samuelson who scores the basket after her great hustle.
videos.headline: UConn gets the rebound and Samuelson with  great effort to get the layup

videos.description: UConn Geno Auriemma happy with the intensity his team played in the first half and to get Crystal Dangerfield back from injury.
videos.headline: UConn coach Geno Auriemma on their big win over Temple
